<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>{تَأْكُلُونَ <span class="c2">(٧٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[٧٩]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«تحملون»</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{آَيَاتِهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٨١]</span> حسن.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
